title: We Are in a New York State of Mind
description:
Tasia is back with Camo this week and dishing on all her adventures in New York City! From having the best salmon in her life to shopping till she drops, to being less than impressed with Atlantic City. Camo and Tasia talk job stress, upcoming changes, and so much more, you won't want to miss it!
Get $20 off your fertility test when you go to ModernFertility.com/unfazed
Watch "Unfazed and Unbothered" on YouTube
If you like the show, telling a friend about it would be helpful! You can text, email, Tweet, or send this link to a friend: https://bit.ly/UnfazedandUnbotheredPodcast
